    <title>MarkDown学习笔记</title>
    <url>/2023-04/da7ed36c/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>学习makedown的笔记，记录用。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h2><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 三级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### 四级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">##### 五级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###### 六级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="note "><h1 id="一级标题"><a href="#一级标题" class="headerlink" title="一级标题"></a>一级标题</h1><h2 id="二级标题"><a href="#二级标题" class="headerlink" title="二级标题"></a>二级标题</h2><h3 id="三级标题"><a href="#三级标题" class="headerlink" title="三级标题"></a>三级标题</h3><h4 id="四级标题"><a href="#四级标题" class="headerlink" title="四级标题"></a>四级标题</h4><h5 id="五级标题"><a href="#五级标题" class="headerlink" title="五级标题"></a>五级标题</h5><h6 id="六级标题"><a href="#六级标题" class="headerlink" title="六级标题"></a>六级标题</h6></div>

<h2 id="强调"><a href="#强调" class="headerlink" title="强调"></a>强调</h2><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*这个是斜体*</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**这个是粗体**</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*这个是粗斜体*</span>**</span>  </span><br><span class="line">~~这个是删除线~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><em>这个是斜体</em><br><strong>这个是粗体</strong><br><em><strong>这个是粗斜体</strong></em><br><del>这个是删除线</del></p>
<h2 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h2><h3 id="无序列表"><a href="#无序列表" class="headerlink" title="无序列表"></a>无序列表</h3><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  *</span> 1.1  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  *</span> 1.2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  *</span> 1.2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>1<ul>
<li>1.1  </li>
<li>1.2</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>2<ul>
<li>1.2</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a>有序列表</h3><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> Item 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> Item 2  </span><br><span class="line">注意，列表前面的序号其实是无关紧要的，渲染时Markdown会自动修改该序号。</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> Item 3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    1.</span> Item 3a</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    2.</span> Item 3b</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> Item 4</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">    *</span> 有序列表下的无序列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ol>
<li>Item 1</li>
<li>Item 2<br>注意，列表前面的序号其实是无关紧要的，渲染时Markdown会自动修改该序号。</li>
<li>Item 3<ol>
<li>Item 3a</li>
<li>Item 3b</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>Item 4<ul>
<li>有序列表下的无序列表</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h2><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 左对齐 | 右对齐 | 居中对齐 |</span><br><span class="line">| :-| -: | :-: |</span><br><span class="line">| 格 | 格 | 格 |</span><br><span class="line">| 格 | 格 | 格 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">左对齐</th>
<th align="right">右对齐</th>
<th align="center">居中对齐</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">格</td>
<td align="right">格</td>
<td align="center">格</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">格</td>
<td align="right">格</td>
<td align="center">格</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h2><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">链接名称</span>](<span class="link">https://www.bilibili.com/</span>)  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">&lt;https://www.bilibili.com/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/">链接名称</a><br><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/">https://www.bilibili.com/</a></p>
<h2 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h2><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt 属性文本</span>](<span class="link">图片地址</span>)</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt 属性文本</span>](<span class="link">图片地址 &quot;可选标题&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">RUNOOB 图标</span>](<span class="link">http://static.runoob.com/images/runoob-logo.png</span>)</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">RUNOOB 图标</span>](<span class="link">http://static.runoob.com/images/runoob-logo.png &quot;RUNOOB&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="http://static.runoob.com/images/runoob-logo.png" alt="RUNOOB 图标"><br><img src="http://static.runoob.com/images/runoob-logo.png" alt="RUNOOB 图标" title="RUNOOB"></p>
<h2 id="任务列表"><a href="#任务列表" class="headerlink" title="任务列表"></a>任务列表</h2><figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> [x] 这个是打勾的任务列表。</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> [ ] 这个是没打勾的任务列表。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 这个是打勾的任务列表。</li>
<li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 这个是没打勾的任务列表。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="Next主题可用代码"><a href="#Next主题可用代码" class="headerlink" title="Next主题可用代码"></a>Next主题可用代码</h2><h3 id="按钮"><a href="#按钮" class="headerlink" title="按钮"></a>按钮</h3><p><a href="https://theme-next.js.org/docs/tag-plugins/button.html">官方教程链接</a></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% button url, text, icon [class], [title] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% btn url, text, icon [class], [title] %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>url：链接地址</li>
<li>text：按钮上的文本</li>
<li>icon：Fontswesome图标名称，如果没有指定文本则为必填项。</li>
<li>[class]：可选。Fontswesome图标种类（<code>fa-fw</code> <code>fa-lg</code> <code>fa-2x</code> <code>fa-3x</code> <code>fa-4x</code> <code>fa-5x</code>)</li>
<li>[title]：可选。鼠标悬停在上面的提示。</li>
</ul>
<p>示例：  </p>
<a class="btn" href="#" title="悬停显示"><i class="fa fa-home fa-lg"></i>按钮文本</a>

<h3 id="图片墙"><a href="#图片墙" class="headerlink" title="图片墙"></a>图片墙</h3><p><a href="https://theme-next.js.org/docs/tag-plugins/group-pictures.html">官方教程链接</a></p>
<h3 id="标签"><a href="#标签" class="headerlink" title="标签"></a>标签</h3><p><a href="https://theme-next.js.org/docs/tag-plugins/label.html">官方教程链接</a></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% label [class]@text %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>[class]：可选。可填以下几个参数<mark class="label default">default</mark>
<mark class="label primary">primary</mark>
<mark class="label success">success</mark>
<mark class="label info">info</mark>
<mark class="label warning">warning</mark>
<mark class="label danger">danger</mark></li>
<li>text：显示的文本。</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="链接组"><a href="#链接组" class="headerlink" title="链接组"></a>链接组</h3><p><a href="https://theme-next.js.org/docs/tag-plugins/link-grid.html">官方教程链接</a></p>
<h3 id="note"><a href="#note" class="headerlink" title="note"></a>note</h3><p><a href="https://theme-next.js.org/docs/tag-plugins/note.html">官方教程链接</a></p>
<figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">不定义样式</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="note "><p>不定义样式</p>
</div>

<figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note default %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">defaul样式</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="note default"><p>defaul样式</p>
</div>

<figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note primary %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">primary样式</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="note primary"><p>primary样式</p>
</div>

<figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note info %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">info样式</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="note info"><p>info样式</p>
</div>

<figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note success %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">success样式</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="note success"><p>success样式</p>
</div>

<figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note warning %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">warning样式</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="note warning"><p>warning样式</p>
</div>

<figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note danger %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">danger样式</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<div class="note danger"><p>danger样式</p>
</div>

<figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note info no-icon 这里是摘要 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">折叠测试，info可以换成其他的，no-icon可以去掉。</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<details class="note info no-icon"><summary><p>这里是摘要</p>
</summary>
<p>折叠测试，info可以换成其他的，no-icon可以去掉。</p>

</details>

<h3 id="选项卡"><a href="#选项卡" class="headerlink" title="选项卡"></a>选项卡</h3><p><a href="https://theme-next.js.org/docs/tag-plugins/tabs.html">官方教程链接</a></p>
]]></content>
